Initially it was only removal of no longer used method from interface.
Now this change makes few other things, which in ideal situation should be done in separate changes. But given that it is way easier to change dbus API in one fell swoop, I'll be okay with that. So let's just settle with the commit message extension, and I will change CR to +2.
Removal of this property should be explained in commit message.

I think it would be worth to note in commit message 
that the "Changed API to be more flexible in the future" part from https://gerrit.openbmc.org/c/openbmc/telemetry/+/55103 
was reverted by this change
